{"2943670": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Night Club Simulator", "steam_appid": 2943670, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接管一個破舊的廢棄場地，將其改造成全國最受歡迎的夜店。在這場冒險中，玩家將翻新、升級並擴展場地的每個角落，以達到夜生活的巔峰。但這不會輕鬆；你需要管理棘手的顧客，同時維護夜店的聲譽。這款遊戲不僅僅是夜店模擬器；它是一場充滿策略、創意和混亂的旅程，與朋友共同體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從場地設計到顧客關係，我們提供了一個動態氛圍，讓你沉浸在夜生活的混亂與刺激之中。創造自己夜店的風格和氛圍，自定義場地，並在夜生活中留下你的印記。不管你是想用現代設計裝飾夜店，還是添加一點懷舊的氣息，選擇完全在你手中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/0665c45ec6ecad5c2ce9d32b1b0c0ecf.webp?t=1761136371\" width=174 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你將體驗過的最佳合作模擬類型的畫面。使用虛幻引擎5開發。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/539faac9578832bce0bd5188d9c54bfb.poster.avif?t=1761136371\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/539faac9578832bce0bd5188d9c54bfb.webm?t=1761136371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/539faac9578832bce0bd5188d9c54bfb.mp4?t=1761136371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/4aaa3ffbd3807821cae686b35545c5a9.webp?t=1761136371\" width=347 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>動態的顧客 AI 行為和自發事件，帶來更加沉浸式的體驗。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/81bd0deb40ef3096cdd511759e60923d.poster.avif?t=1761136371\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/81bd0deb40ef3096cdd511759e60923d.webm?t=1761136371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/81bd0deb40ef3096cdd511759e60923d.mp4?t=1761136371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/f00892cdf7ad2e8a3c2ac9a29c8a2fc8.webp?t=1761136371\" width=224 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>通過增加脫衣舞者、保險套販賣機和其他高級設施來提高夜店的聲譽和顧客滿意度。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/e59346fef844c0e63d6bf0d25f4430ce.poster.avif?t=1761136371\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/e59346fef844c0e63d6bf0d25f4430ce.webm?t=1761136371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/e59346fef844c0e63d6bf0d25f4430ce.mp4?t=1761136371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/743b3af9324c7f1109afd112ecc9b1aa.webp?t=1761136371\" width=301 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理誰可以進入並收取入場費，以保持控制並最大化門票收入。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943670/extras/